00:37:29.519 --> 00:37:30.400
adakah utusan Nanzhao

00:37:30.679 --> 00:37:32.920
pernah jumpa Master Shenguan seorang diri?

00:37:33.159 --> 00:37:35.599
Para pegawai Tang Agung sentiasa bersamanya.

00:37:35.880 --> 00:37:37.000
Tiada mesyuarat tertutup yang diadakan.

00:37:42.679 --> 00:37:43.280
Tuan,

00:37:43.760 --> 00:37:44.800
sesuatu telah berlaku.

00:37:45.039 --> 00:37:46.239
Komando Putera An ditemui

00:37:46.240 --> 00:37:47.900
Mayat Tuan Shenguan
